{
  "name": "my-v0-project",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "private": true,
  "scripts": {
    "build": "next build",
    "dev": "next dev",
    "lint": "eslint .",
    "start": "next start",
    "electron-dev": "npx concurrently \"npm run dev\" \"npx wait-on tcp:3000 && npm run electron\"",
    "build:ui": "next build",
    "package": "npm run build:ui && electron-builder --win",
    "postinstall": "electron-builder install-app-deps"
  },
  "main": "main.js",
  "author": "OpenWrt Manager Team",
  "description": "Desktop manager for OpenWrt devices",
  "build": {
    "appId": "com.openwrt.manager",
    "productName": "OpenWrt Manager",
    "npmRebuild": false,
    "directories": {
      "output": "dist"
    },
    "files": [
      "main.js",
      "out/**/*",
      "package.json",
      "!node_modules"
    ],
    "extraResources": [
      {
        "from": "../backend/dist/backend.exe",
        "to": "backend.exe"
      }
    ],
    "win": {
      "target": "nsis",
      "icon": "public/favicon.ico"
    }
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@hookform/resolvers": "^3.10.0",
    "@radix-ui/react-accordion": "1.2.2",
    "@radix-ui/react-alert-dialog": "1.1.4",
    "@radix-ui/react-aspect-ratio": "1.1.1",
    "@radix-ui/react-avatar": "1.1.2",
    "@radix-ui/react-checkbox": "1.1.3",
    "@radix-ui/react-collapsible": "1.1.2",
    "@radix-ui/react-context-menu": "2.2.4",
    "@radix-ui/react-dialog": "1.1.4",
    "@radix-ui/react-dropdown-menu": "2.1.4",
    "@radix-ui/react-hover-card": "1.1.4",
    "@radix-ui/react-label": "2.1.1",
    "@radix-ui/react-menubar": "1.1.4",
    "@radix-ui/react-navigation-menu": "1.2.3",
    "@radix-ui/react-popover": "1.1.4",
    "@radix-ui/react-progress": "1.1.1",
    "@radix-ui/react-radio-group": "1.2.2",
    "@radix-ui/react-scroll-area": "1.2.2",
    "@radix-ui/react-select": "2.1.4",
    "@radix-ui/react-separator": "1.1.1",
    "@radix-ui/react-slider": "1.2.2",
    "@radix-ui/react-slot": "1.1.1",
    "@radix-ui/react-switch": "1.1.2",
    "@radix-ui/react-tabs": "1.1.2",
    "@radix-ui/react-toast": "1.2.4",
    "@radix-ui/react-toggle": "1.1.1",
    "@radix-ui/react-toggle-group": "1.1.1",
    "@radix-ui/react-tooltip": "1.1.6",
    "@vercel/analytics": "1.3.1",
    "autoprefixer": "^10.4.20",
    "class-variance-authority": "^0.7.1",
    "clsx": "^2.1.1",
    "cmdk": "1.0.4",
    "date-fns": "4.1.0",
    "embla-carousel-react": "8.5.1",
    "input-otp": "1.4.1",
    "lucide-react": "^0.454.0",
    "next": "16.0.10",
    "next-themes": "^0.4.6",
    "react": "19.2.0",
    "react-day-picker": "9.8.0",
    "react-dom": "19.2.0",
    "react-hook-form": "^7.60.0",
    "react-resizable-panels": "^2.1.7",
    "recharts": "2.15.4",
    "sonner": "^1.7.4",
    "tailwind-merge": "^3.3.1",
    "tailwindcss-animate": "^1.0.7",
    "vaul": "^1.1.2",
    "zod": "3.25.76",
    "@tailwindcss/postcss": "^4.1.9",
    "@types/node": "^22",
    "@types/react": "^19",
    "@types/react-dom": "^19",
    "concurrently": "^8.2.0",
    "electron": "^28.0.0",
    "electron-builder": "^26.0.12",
    "postcss": "^8.5",
    "rimraf": "^6.1.2",
    "tailwindcss": "^4.1.9",
    "tw-animate-css": "1.3.3",
    "typescript": "^5",
    "wait-on": "^7.2.0"
  }
}
